publisher			Prexen Studios							
publish_time	 2015年4月1日		
desc_long							评测						“Gare combines the aesthetics of Tron, the gameplay of the venerable arena shooter genre, the mazes of Berserk and those Mechs everyone seems to be so fond of in one lovely action game definitely worth your time. Gare, you see, detailed wireframe visuals and atmospheric soundtrack aside, is a most addictive game with some simple yet satisfying upgrade mechanics...”Indiegames.com												关于这款游戏							A polished top down action shooter set in a digital like world with upgradable mechs.Vitris-47 has been the central stage of many conflicts over the ages. The Idalin empire rules over the planet with an ironhand and war is always present. On the other side, there´s the resistance, trying to retake the planet to its former glory and you are part of it.Driving your mech around the gorgeous digital cityscapes of the planet, the time has come for a new power to arise and put an end to this war.						
title	 Gare Sapphire Mechs			
